                <p>Choose from a wide range of beautiful, functional venues that fit every occasion and capacity.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="p-4 border rounded text-center h-100">
                <h5>Event Decoration</h5>
                <p>Customized themes, professional décor, and elegant aesthetics that wow your guests.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="p-4 border rounded text-center h-100">
                <h5>Service Packages</h5>
                <p>From catering to photography, we offer complete packages tailored to your event needs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

